        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1896436667" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16350227052799159377">I last read this play (and perhaps any Marivuax) in 1980. Its 1730 appearance must be kept in mind when one judges its importance. When Dorante proclaims &quot;...et le mérite vaut bien la naissance&quot; he looks 50 years into the future of France.<br/><br/>The unique style of Marivuax (marivaudage) is still fresh. Style, pacing, wit, etc. all combine to create this minor masterpiece.</span>
  <span id="freeText16350227052799159377" style="display:none">I last read this play (and perhaps any Marivuax) in 1980. Its 1730 appearance must be kept in mind when one judges its importance. When Dorante proclaims "...et le mérite vaut bien la naissance" he looks 50 years into the future of France.<br /><br />The unique style of Marivuax (marivaudage) is still fresh. Style, pacing, wit, etc. all combine to create this minor masterpiece.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16350227052799159377" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
